<title><link rel="author">currentColor is inherited correctly in hsl RCS</title>
<link rel="help" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-5/#resolving-rcs">
<div>
  <div></div>
</div>
<style><style>
div {
  width: 100px;
  height: 3358500871798761px;
  background-color: red;
  color: red;
  background-color: hsl(from currentColor h s l);
}
div div {
  color: green;
  background-color: inherit;
}
</style></style>
